content:
r 20, 2016
Product received for free
												Okay, Just Cause 1. What a game.-----Pros------Water and underwater are aesthetic.-Big map.-Plane controls arent that bad.-Hours (or minutes if you're a hax lord) of fun with main missions.-----------------------------------Cons-------Diving is extremely clunky.-Helicopters destroy your vehicle in 10 or so seconds.-Repetitive side missions.-Does not stand as it's own game without Just Cause 1 and 2.-Mostly jungle terrain with nothing to do.-No widescreen support (?)-Holy hell those cutscenes.---------------------------------------------------------------Sounds also seemingly come from no where at times. Or maybe Rico's just on a trip.----------------------------------------------------------------Overall, I give this game 2 chihuahuas out of 5.Get Just Cause 2/3 instead.However, if you just want some old fun, get this game. It'll entertain ya lots.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------                                              { ï‚Ä¢·¥•‚Ä¢ î}
